_sText:
my original Knife arena map KA_kingdom converted into gg_kingdom

max players - 50

Color correction is used in this map

after 55 seconds, players must meet at the bottom or they will be killed by a nerve gas released into the map

This map has a lightmap grid of 8, meaning that the shadows are sharper and better looking then your default map.

It is ergonomic and easy to play on and has over 50 player spawns.

Please enjoy thoroughly!

P.S. there is custom sounds as well as custom textures used in this map
